Title: An Act Changing the Name of Barangay Barucboc Sur in the Municipality of Mallig, Province of Isabela, to Barangay San Pedro
Data:
BATAS PAMBANSA Blg. 609
An Act Changing the Name of Barangay Barucboc Sur in the Municipality of Mallig, Province of Isabela, to Barangay San Pedro
Section 1. The name of Barangay Barucboc Sur in the Municipality of Mallig, Province of Isabela, is changed to Barangay San Pedro.
Section 2. This Act shall take effect upon its approval.
Approved: June 24, 1983
